Interface RMIEventListenerI

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote

    public interface RMIEventListenerI
extends java.rmi.Remote
    This interface need not supply anything to do its job. It brings the TestEventListener interface together with Remote so that we can have RMI-based event handlers for tests
